CustomField.description: Indicates that there is a data error on a related Payee Pay Batch record. This is raised as a warning. A warning can be bypassed if the Enforce Flag Validation custom setting (Payroll_Configuration__c.Enforce_Flag_Validation__c) is set to False.

CustomField.label: Error on PayBatchItem
